      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for explaining. i guess i'm just wondering about the \"opponents\" part specifically... a lot of the parents in our local facebook group are saying the school is basically pushing an agenda and being disrespectful to how we raise our kids. do they have any actual points that make sense, or is it mostly just people being difficult about progress?",
